{"tid":1997091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一早鑽漏洞]回應牌照持有人是否其直系親屬　陶輝反問直系親屬定義","createTime":"2020-05-01T11:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T14:11:51.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"69299629fa0053e4c2a6fafa2b419299de934b18","tid":1997091,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523792-20200501.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523792-20200501.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw17Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=d443f7a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523792-20200501.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9c459fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523792-20200501.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n助理警務處處長陶輝居住在清水灣碧水新村的牌照屋，被質疑違反牌照條款及佔用官地。<br />\n<br />\n陶輝在寓所外被追問事件時表示，他居住的1號屋是牌照屋，他得到牌照持有人的批准住在該處，而該牌照持有人為他妻子的親人。被問到牌照持有人是否他們的直系親屬，他反問直系親屬的定義，又指會是有趣的發現。<br />\n<br />\n陶輝又說，希望地政總署等有關部門可以有一個全面的調查，他會配合調查結果，若地政總署要求他離開，他會照做，但他很希望當局說明「親人」的定義。"},{"pid":"dcf0d2e75acf4ee3c4bd31b36bb2bc9b76efeb30","tid":1997091,"uid":196924,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"做咗咁多年公墓猿<br />\n邊個家庭成員有得跟你食醫療福利，邊個咪係香港政府定義嘅直系囉"},{"pid":"f9df9f16f747e8befc4d0f9bbbfb75549f3fad61","tid":1997091,"uid":41861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:49:47.000Z","msg":"反問個官啦"},{"pid":"ef1afdf5d3266b0356bc1f8e60c865749bb47898","tid":1997091,"uid":37912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:53:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbc776da47d5f08ef9fb99e2d6f1cf30ae094228","tid":1997091,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"唔係應該立即停職先咩"},{"pid":"7dc6e16055851792adcd8b6a4ad177